00:00:20.076 --> 00:00:24.937
What are you going to cook for us today?
Chukkakura Baby Potato

00:00:31.453 --> 00:00:34.779
Ingredients required for Chukkakura Baby Potato

00:00:35.048 --> 00:00:51.099
Green Sorrel Leaves, Baby Potatoes, Dry Red Chillies,
 Raw Bengal Gram, Ginger Garlic Paste, 
Fenugreek Seeds Powder, Coriander Seeds Powder, 
Coriander Leaves, Salt, Red Chilli Powder, Turmeric Powder &amp; Oil

00:01:01.522 --> 00:01:06.988
First heat some oil in a pan

00:01:19.211 --> 00:01:23.858
Take some green sorrel leaves, 
clean them and cut them into pieces
 &amp; keep them aside

00:01:25.884 --> 00:01:37.999
Take some baby potatoes, 
peel them and keep them aside

00:01:53.607 --> 00:02:02.869
Add some dry red chillies, mustard seeds, 
fenu greek seeds and black gram into the pan

00:02:11.695 --> 00:02:19.203
Add five sliced green chillies and three chopped onions
 into the pan &amp; fry them for a while

00:02:32.457 --> 00:02:38.851
Soak some bengal gram in water for
 an hour and add them into the pan

00:02:41.285 --> 00:02:46.264
Add some ginger garlic paste into the pan &amp; mix well

00:02:48.621 --> 00:02:52.279
Add some turmeric powder into the pan &amp; mix well

00:02:55.077 --> 00:03:02.030
Add the sliced green sorrel leaves
 into the pan &amp; mix well

00:03:22.519 --> 00:03:27.072
Add some red chilli powder into the cooked green sorrel leaves

00:03:36.637 --> 00:03:40.428
Add some salt into the cooked sorrel leaves &amp; mix well

00:03:49.967 --> 00:03:55.585
Add a pinch of fenugreek powder into the pan &amp; mix well

00:04:07.785 --> 00:04:16.119
Add two tea spoons of coriander powder
 into the pan &amp; mix well

00:04:24.979 --> 00:04:27.335
Now close the pan with a lid 
&amp; let it cook for a while

00:04:28.243 --> 00:04:40.353
Heat some oil in another pan 
&amp; fry some baby potatoes in it

00:04:45.349 --> 00:04:52.344
Remove the fried potato pieces into a bowl 

00:04:55.867 --> 00:05:00.581
Add the fried potato pieces into the cooked sorrel leaves mix

00:05:05.227 --> 00:05:08.433
Now mix them well 

00:05:13.700 --> 00:05:17.296
Take the Chikkakura Baby Potato into a serving bowl

00:05:18.459 --> 00:05:21.985
Top the dish with some coriander leaves 

